title: Eminem Full Discography [Flac] *RARE*
description:
*DISCLAIMER* The original ".Torrent" was too big to upload so download this and a ".txt" file WILL be in there including an adfly link, also I tried to change the piece size, but it didn't work. Good luck Sorry, I DID lose the ".cue" sheets, but you can check them yourself, they're what I listed them as! Also Most of the Mixtapes ARE ".mp3" format, be aware that not ALL of it is in ".flac". The first, second, third, fourth, fifth columns and the first seven mixtapes listed are in ".flac" format, disincluding Shady XV, which is in ".mp3" format, both disks at 320 KBps. Also me and a couple of friends, Maxdapeice, Me (Jeremy10001000) and FreDroDaGod have added OUR custom made "The Shady Shizzle Collection", it is in ".m4a" format! And last, but
